snippet.title: CloudKid
snippet.description:
This is CloudKid.

Not defined by genres, CloudKid is here to support thriving undiscovered talent showcased with a unique audiovisual experience.

CloudKid is for those who are not afraid to be themselves; for those who set no limits; for those who need an escape.

Keep your head in the Clouds
